<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscribe to <%= TWITCH_HANDLE %>'s Twitch Channel</title>
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .subscribe-button {
            background-color: #9147ff;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .subscribe-button:hover {
            background-color: #772ce8;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Subscribe to <%= TWITCH_HANDLE %>'s Twitch Channel</h1>
        <p>You need to subscribe to gain full access to our site features. Once you have subscribed, you will be redirected...</p>
        <a href="<%= subscribeUrl %>" target="_blank" class="button">
            Subscribe Now on Twitch
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
